Condition.name: GET9isCMHasProblemItemCreatable
Condition.expression: Condition::isCMHasProblemItemCreatable(p,s,u) AND u.role_name="Services Engineer" OR u.role_name="Services Engineering Manager" AND s.last_release_status!=NULL AND ( (Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForPrimary(p,u) AND Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u)) OR (Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForPrimary(p,u) AND (Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u))) OR (Condition::GET6isClassificationRestrictedForPrimary(p,u) AND (Condition::GET6isClassificationRestrictedForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u))))

Condition.name: GET9isCMHasSolutionItemCreatable
Condition.expression: Condition::isCMHasSolutionItemCreatable(p,s,u) AND (u.role_name="Services Engineer" OR u.role_name="Services Engineering Manager") AND s.last_release_status=NULL AND((Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForPrimary(p,u) AND Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u)) OR (Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForPrimary(p,u) AND (Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u))) OR (Condition::GET6isClassificationRestrictedForPrimary(p,u) AND (Condition::GET6isClassificationRestrictedForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u))))

Condition.name: GET9isCMImplementsCreatable
Condition.expression: Condition::isActiveSequence(p) AND Condition::isCMImplementsCreatableForPrimary(p, u) AND Condition::isCMImplementsCreatableForSecondary(s, u) AND Condition::isAuthor(u)

Condition.name: GET9isCMImplementsCreatableForPrimary
Condition.expression: (Condition::isRequestor(o, u) AND o.CMClosure = "Open" AND o.CMDisposition = "None" AND o.CMMaturity = "Elaborating") OR (Condition::isChangeSpecialist1(o, u) AND ((o.CMClosure = "Open" AND o.CMDisposition = "None" AND o.CMMaturity = "Elaborating") OR (o.CMClosure = "Open" AND o.CMDisposition = "Investigate" AND o.CMMaturity = "Reviewing")))

Condition.name: GET9isCMhasImpactedItemCreatable
Condition.expression: Condition::isCMHasImpactedItemCreatable(p,s,u) AND u.role_name="Services Engineer" OR u.role_name="Services Engineering Manager" AND s.last_release_status!=NULL AND ( (Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForPrimary(p,u) AND Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u)) OR (Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForPrimary(p,u) AND (Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u))) OR (Condition::GET6isClassificationRestrictedForPrimary(p,u) AND (Condition::GET6isClassificationRestrictedForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u))))
